name: Helen Swerry
description:
I am a tender and romantic woman. I wish to admit that I am a woman who knows exactly what she needs in her life and doesn’t want to loose time in vain. I like to care about people who are close to me! I have a lot of love in my heart and I want to give it to someone.
As for me, ideal relations is when people easily can find an agreement, when man can listen and lady can understand. When man can be romantic and lady can be passionate. Of course I want to be with a successful man but I don’t care about the age and status of him, because the most important is love.
